		</a>
	</li>

				<li class="tab__menu-item js-tab__item ">
		<a href="/en/pb/hansard-debates/rhr/combined/HansD_20160921_20160921/tab/relateddocuments" data-ajax-url="/en/ajax/hansardcombineddetail/6227/HansD_20160921_20160921/relateddocuments" class="tab__menu-link js-tab__link">
			Related Documents
