							<body  ><div class="section"><p class="VoteReason">A party vote was called for on the question,<em> </em><em>That</em><em> the </em><em>Public Works (Prohibition of Compulsory Acquisition of Māori Land) Amendment Bill be now read a first time</em><em>.</em></p><p class="VoteCount"><strong>Ayes 48</strong></p><p class="VoteText">New Zealand Labour 32; Green Party 14; Māori Party 2.</p><p class="VoteCount"><strong>Noes 73</strong></p><p class="VoteText">New Zealand National 59; New Zealand First 12; ACT New Zealand 1; United Future 1.</p><p class="VoteResult">Motion not agreed to.</p></div></body>
